Grant conditions

Final candidates will be notified of selection no earlier than
May  1,  1994.  Grants will begin in the U.S.  no earlier than
September 1,  1994. Grantees will receive a stipend, roundtrip
air   transportation   to   the  United  States,  and  medical
insurance. Travel by family members is not covered.

Grant applications  will  not  be   returned.   All   official
communications  about  the  results of the competition will be
sent by mail.




